features: 🔌【Side Table with Charging Station】This unique small end table is designed with a modern industrial look, suitable for lots of decorative styles. Besides, our bedside tables come with a charging station which is designed on the second layer to avoid accidents caused by spilled drinks.

🔋【2 x USB Ports & 2 x 3-Prong Power Outlets】Low Battery Where is Power Outlet? It’s just within your arm’s reach. The charging station of the slim end table can charge 4 devices simultaneously. 6.5 ft power supply cord also provides great convenience.

🔧【Easy to Assemble】With the simple structure and accessories marked with numbers, you can easily assemble the narrow side table within 15 minutes with the detailed instruction and tools in the package. You can also assemble the couch side table refer to the installation video in the product page. Dimension: 15.75"(L) x 10.24"(W) x 23.62"(H)

🅲【C Shaped Design】 The C table is easy to slide into the underside of the sofa, bed or chair, offering you convenient access to your snacks, drinks, phone, tablet, etc. Meanwhile, the skinny design also makes it perfect for small spaces. NOTE: the thickness of the metal base including the below foot pad is 1.1".

💪【Sturdy & Durable】Yoobure end tables for living room and bedroom are composed of durable particle board and sturdy steel frame to provide long-lasting durability and sturdiness, supporting up to 100 lbs.

😊【One Year Warrant】In order to ensure our customers receive 100% satisfactory service, we provide a One-year Warranty for our C Shaped End Table with Charging Station. Any quality problem, assemble problem or missing part about the end tables please don't hesitate to contact us.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice table, but outlet has difficult functionality
reviews.reviewText: UPDATE - I'd like to note that the company reached out to me after reading my review, asking what they could do to make my purchase experience a more positive one. They offered to send me a new replacement outlet part at no cost. I installed the new outlet into the stand once it arrived and it is a bit better (less tight) than the original one.Original review - I like the table, it works well for small, tight spaces. It's stable and relatively strong and it has a nice appearance.However, I do have one big complaint - the outlets are very tight. Whenever I was try and unplug any electrical charger, I have to tank on it very hard to get it out. Given that this is happening under the table top, more often than not I slam my hand into the underside of the table hurting it (even when trying to be careful). This is a huge drawback and it's already driving me crazy just a few weeks into owning the table.We did, btw, install casters on the leg bottoms in order to allow it to slide more easily (an idea I took from another reviewer). The casters install really easily if you buy stem ones that insert right into the existing feet holes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best ready to assemble furniture ever.
reviews.reviewText: We bought two of your powered chair side tables. I wanted to thank you. The product was well thought out, the instructions were spot on, the parts were all labeled and in bags, and the finished product is sturdy. I have never assembled a better furniture kit. The parts all fit. There was one extra screw in each bag and the supplied tools worked well. In short, I give these products a 100% five star rating. Thank you for a high quality product at a great price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This was very easy to build. We have a small living space in our office area and this was a preferable table to a coffee table because it allowed us to move it around and save space. The overhand of the "C" is quite the perfect amount for a 3-person sofa that we have. We can put it between my wife and myself with drinks and snacks in the middle of us. Additionally, the plug and USB were helpful for charging our phones or for plugging in my wife's heated blanket! Very happy with this
